<div class="container">
  <h1> Contributing </h1>
  <p> Fedora Developer Portal is a community effort to share guides and information about open-source development. And we need your help!</p>

  <br>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2 class="panel-title"> <strong>1.</strong> Find out what's needed </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p> We use the issue tracker in our content repository to keep track of pages we would like to include on the portal. Search for the <span class="label label-success">help wanted</span> tag to find what's needed.</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/developer-portal/content/labels/help%20wanted" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Browse issues</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2 class="panel-title"> <strong>2.</strong> Read the contribution guidelines </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p> We have written a contribution guidelines describing the basic structure of our repository, instructions about writing a content, and some general tips.</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/developer-portal/content/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Read the contribution guidelines</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2 class="panel-title"> <strong>3.</strong> Learn markdown </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p> We use the markdown syntax to write the content. </p>
      <a href="https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Learn markdown</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2 class="panel-title"> <strong>4.</strong> Fork and make changes </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p> Now you need to fork the <a href="https://github.com/developer-portal/content">content repository</a> and make all changes you want. To do so, visit the repository and just click fork in the top-right corner.</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/developer-portal/content" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Visit the content repo</a>
      <a href="https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">Learn about forking</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h2 class="panel-title"> <strong>5.</strong> Send us a pull-request </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p> When you're done, send us a pull request and someone will make a review. When is everything ready, your contribution will be merged and eventualy published on the portal. </p>
      <a href="https://github.com/developer-portal/content" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Visit the content repo</a>
      <a href="https://help.github.com/articles/using-pull-requests/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-sm">Learn about pull-requests</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
